htmail-view (0.5) unstable; urgency=low

  * [htmail-decode] Handle non-multipart messages (text/html).
  * [htmail-view] Remove open-link* menu items from context menu.
  * [htmail-view] Remove background of toolbar.
  * [htmail-view] Workaround for URI 1.60: missing has_recognized_scheme method.
  * [htmail-*] Allow detach htmail-decode/-view from terminal.

 -- Thomas Liske <thomas@fiasko-nw.net>  

htmail-view (0.4.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * [htmail-decode] Install htmail-decode into /usr/bin/.

 -- Thomas Liske <thomas@fiasko-nw.net>  Thu, 08 Oct 2015 12:00:19 +0200

htmail-view (0.4) unstable; urgency=low

  * [htmail-decode] MIME decoder launching htmail-viewer.
  * [htmail-view] Add MIME mode allowing to access resources referenced
    by Content-IDs (used by htmail-decode).
  * [htmail-view] Add print dialog.
  * [htmail-view] Keep focus on WebKit view to enable scrolling by
    keyboard.

 -- Thomas Liske <thomas@fiasko-nw.net>  Sun, 04 Oct 2015 09:39:08 +0200

htmail-view (0.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add mime-support file (Debian).
  * Enable WebKit privacy settings.
  * [Bug] Fix links with @target="_blank" did nothing.

 -- Thomas Liske <thomas@fiasko-nw.net>  Tue, 29 Sep 2015 23:50:32 +0200

htmail-view (0.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add accelerator keys:
    - q: quit htmail-view
    - r: toggle remote resources
  * Add getopts handling.
  * Add verbose mode.
  * Add wmctrl wrapper (focus handling).
  * Ignore policy requests not triggered by link-clicked.
  * Improve window handling:
    - bring to front on start
    - set reasonable title
    - show destinitations of links
    - use a standard icon
  * Rename project to htmail-view.

 -- Thomas Liske <thomas@fiasko-nw.net>  Sun, 27 Sep 2015 11:58:45 +0200

